title: What is Duidui
subtitle: Duidui is my work for this class!
detail: Duidui is a name I made up for my project in this class. I wanted a cute and catchy name that represents my work. Duidui doesn't have a specific meaning, but it sounds fun and memorable (∩^o^)⊃━☆

title: What is Duidui means
subtitle: Duidui doesn't have meaning, it's just a name(❁´◡`❁)
detail: The name Duidui is simply a playful and imaginative creation. It doesn't have any roots in existing words or languages, but it captures the essence of creativity and fun that I wanted to convey through my project *(੭*ˊᵕˋ)੭*ଘ

title: Why Duidui
subtitle: Because I like the sound of this name! (｡•̀ᴗ-)✧
detail: I chose the name Duidui because I found it to be catchy and easy to remember. The repetition of the syllable 'dui' gives it a rhythmic quality that I find appealing. Overall, Duidui felt like the perfect fit for my project ( •̀ .̫ •́ )✧
